
%% Class Diagram: Skill Domain
%% Source: app/models/skill.ts, user_skill.ts, task_required_skill.ts,
%%         recruiter_bookmark.ts
%% Scope: Columns match @column decorators exactly.
%%         ⚡ = leaked static method (should → Repository layer).
